@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ovijnd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.cos(v0) + ((tmp + 0.97 - v0 + 0.61) * 0.90))
    tmp = (tmp + (v0 / v2))
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v1 + 0.11) - (v1 + 0.45 - v0 + 0.70)))
    v0 = 0.45
    data[tid] = v0
